The,MSG,Send,SMS,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,transactional,or,bulk,SMS,into,their,apps,This,service,can,scale,to,send,tens,or,millions,of,messages,as,needed,MSG,provides,searchable,logs,and,tags,that,help,users,keep,track,of,what,s,happening,with,their,SMS,Once,the,user,s,mobile,number,is,verified,no,double,verification,is,ever,required